{"type":"text","id":"paneltext","x":924,"y":308,"width":312,"height":224,"text":"M1 — pilot (fully onsite):\n  • Lab = PIC (operates the LIS)\n  • LabSolution = NEITHER PIC nor PIP*\n  • NPC: LabSolution corporate filing only\n  • Breach: lab notifies NPC; vendor enables\n\nM3 — post-pilot central-sync spoke:\n  • Lab = still PIC\n  • LabSolution = PIP (physical custody)\n  • NPC: own aggregation DPS (NPCRS)\n  • Breach: own SIM policy + team + report\n\n* M1 'neither' is fact-dependent — confirm w/ counsel","fontSize":11,"strokeColor":"#7a3a08","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top"},
